lead_paragraph: Tiger Woods will not hit a single shot in competition at this week's Ryder Cup but he has already played a significant and passionate role for the United States as a vice-captain, according to Brandt Snedeker.

headline.print_headline: Tiger Has 'Passion' as a Cup Vice-Captain, Says Snedeker
